<div class="title">Dos and Donts (all you need to know)</div>
<div class="substance">2C-I & MDMA</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Anonymou5&Exact=1">Anonymou5</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Anonymou5. "Dos and Donts (all you need to know): An Experience with 2C-I & MDMA (exp82467)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Feb 2, 2010. erowid.org/exp/82467</div>

<br/>



